dct_title_s: Chart of the Antarctic Ocean : between--latitudes 66° S. and 83° S. and--longitudes 150° E. and 150° W showing the land to the south of 74° S.
dct_description_sm: Inset: track of the discovery.; Relief shown by hachures, spot heights; depth by soundings.; Shows dates and routes taken from Port Lyttelton, New Zealand to King Edward VII Land via Victoria Land on the ship of "Discovery."
dct_creator_sm: Mulock, George F. A. (George Francis Arthur), 1882-1963
